@startuml 124_Assistant
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1
hide footbox

actor User as "User"
participant "HomePage" as UI
participant "Route Handler" as API
participant "Google SDK" as SDK
entity "Gemini (Google) Service" as Gemini

User -> UI : 1. Click balloon chat icon
activate User
activate UI
UI -> UI : 2. Show chat widget
activate UI
deactivate UI

opt Fields left empty
    UI --> User : 2.1 Prompt to fill in required fields
end

User -> UI : 3. Enter prompt & Send

UI -> API : 4. POST {message, history, image}
activate API

API -> Gemini : 5. Fetch available models list (REST API)
activate Gemini
Gemini --> API : 6. Return listJson.models
deactivate Gemini

alt No appropriate AI model found
    API --> UI : 6.1. Return 502 (Error: No model available)
    UI --> User : 6.1.1 Show "The service is currently unavailable" error
else Model found
    API -> SDK : 6.2. model.generateContent({contents, generationConfig})
    activate SDK

    SDK -> Gemini : 6.2.1. Send Request
    activate Gemini
    Gemini --> SDK : 6.2.2. Return Result Object
    deactivate Gemini

    SDK --> API : 6.2.3. Return Response Text
    deactivate SDK

    API --> UI : 6.2.4. Return JSON {success: true, data: text}
    deactivate API

    UI --> User : 6.2.5. Display Response (Plain Text)
    deactivate UI
    deactivate User
end
@enduml